Anooraq, Anglo American Platinum in Talks on Review of Bokoni Structures

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-13T12:04:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/anooraq-anglo-american-platinum-in-talks-on-review-of-bokoni-structures.html
Anooraq Resources Corp. (ARQ)  said it
started talks with Anglo American Platinum Ltd. relating to a
strategic review by the companies of the assets and funding
structures of Bokoni Platinum Holdings Ltd.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  